Name: CodeListID
Description: The ID of the code list (controlled vocabulary) that the content was taken from.

Name: CodeListName_string
Description: The name of the code list.

Name: CodeListAgencyName
Description: The name of the agency maintaining the code list.

Name: CodeListVersionID
Description: The version number of the code list (default is 1.0).

Name: OtherValue
Description: If the value of the string is "Other" or the equivalent from the codelist, this attribute can provide a more specific value not found in the codelist.

Name: CodeListSchemeURN
Description: If maintained within a scheme, the URN of the scheme containing the codelist.
